definition: nefunguje / nedarí sa / nejde / nedá sa
gloss: does not work / it can not / can not / can not be

definition: Hovorí Vaše dieťa o prežitých udalostiach a o veciach a ľuďoch na ktoré si spomína?
gloss: does your child ever talk about past events or people who are not present?

definition: Stalo sa že dieťa hovorilo o udalostiach ktoré sa majú stať v budúcnosti? Napríklad povedalo tutú predtým ako ste išli na cestu (hojda keď ste sa chystali do parku)?
gloss: does your child ever talk about something that's going to happen in the future?

definition: Hovorí Vaše dieťa o veciach ktoré nie sú práve v jeho blízkom okolí (ktoré nevidí a nepočuje)?
gloss: does your child talk a bout objects that are not present?

definition: Pomenúva Vaše dieťa komu veci patria / aj keď osoba nie je práve prítomná? Napríklad vidí mamine topánky a povie mama?
gloss: does your child understand if you ask for something that is not in the room?

definition: Rozumie Vaše dieťa ak sa pýtate na neprítomné veci? Napríklad donesie macka z druhej izby ak poviete Kde je macko?
gloss: does your child ever pick up or point to an object and name an absent person to whom the object belongs?

definition: Keď Vaše dieťa hovorí o sebe čo povie? 1) Číta 2) Janka / Maťko číta 3) čítam / ja čítam
gloss: When your child talks about himself / what does he say? 1) Reads 2) Janka / mother read 3) I read / I am reading

gloss: Sometimes replaces your baby naming things and people in other words?For example / instead hairstyle midwife tells her hairstyle; instead we take maca say we take him?

gloss: What we do something? or go? child responds / for example / hang out / vacuum cleaner / spoon ... by bus / train / car ...

gloss: Where's it going? Where we or something? child responds / for example / to work / to the park in a stroller in lotions ..

gloss: what they're doing / using the forms of words such as papám / I read / I draw / I'm going / dancing ...

gloss: what happened in the past / using the forms of words such as written / stood up / dropped / we played / we read / we have drawn ...

gloss: what happens in the future / using the forms of words such as do / she draws / reverses / she arranges / and bathe ...

gloss: what will happen in the future / use forms of words such as I draw / I'll do / I'll wash / I will save / to reverse / it will wash ...

gloss: slightly requests using forms of words such as come / see / stop / give / look us stand / let ...

definition: hovorí o tom že nejaká činnosť je skončená; používa tvary ako napríklad (je) zatvorený; (je) otvorený; (je) nakreslený; (je) upečené…
gloss: says that an activity is complete / use shapes such as (a) is closed (is) open / (is) drawn (is) baked ...

gloss: wants to say something to someone belongs / it uses words like dad / feline / mom / Zabkiel / grandfathers grasshoppers ...

I stand / stands (instead of standing one)
I make a mistake (instead will make a mistake)

gloss: if he wants to catch / get your attention: 1) child tells and / AHA guidelines and show example to maca2) and / aha there Maco 3) and / AHA / see there is Maco 4) See how Maco Papa

gloss: when he asks to name things: 1) a child asks this / that / what? and shows the subject 2) What is it? / What is it? 3) Let's see what it is? 4) the drinking bird / giraffe?

keď pomenúva miesto: 1) tam/tu 2) tam/tu je maco 3) tam/tu je malý maco 4) tu je taký veľký maco aj tu je

gloss: when speaking about the situation: 1) Variable 2) cooks polievočku 3) mama cooked vegetable polievočku 4) mama cooked and then we Papay

definition: Predstiera Vaše dieťa / že mieša lyžičkou alebo pije z pohára bez použitia predmetov?
gloss: Your child pretends to stir a drink from a cup.

gloss: Your child pretends to play mom / feeding an apple while using a cube / or gives a baby thermometer under his arm while using a pen?
